NEW FEATURES
------------------------------------------------

1. Thumbnail Toggle
   - New setting added to enable or disable thumbnails
     in search results.
   - Find this option in Settings.

2. Voice Search
   - Search using your voice directly from the search
     dialog.
   - Setup: Go to Settings > Select a language > Restart
