3. Voice Recorder - Quality Settings
   Three new options have been added to the voice
   recorder tool:

   a) Bitrate Selection
      - Choose a bitrate that suits your needs.
      - Higher bitrate = better quality but larger file
        size.

   b) Output Format Selection
      - Pick your preferred audio format.
      - Supported formats: MP3, WAV, M4A, OPUS, FLAC,
        AAC, and more.

   c) Output Path Selection
      - Choose where your recordings are saved.

4. Translation Support
   - Translate transcripts, descriptions, and other
     major sections within the app.

5. Bug Fixes
   - Fixed freezing issue during playback.
   - Fixed lag and errors during downloads.
   - Fixed various bugs in search results.

================================================

EXTRA TOOLS
------------------------------------------------

1. AI Image Editor (Major Update)
   - Upload any image and transform it using AI.
   - Powered by NanoBanana Pro.
   - Write a simple prompt describing the changes you
     want.
   - Click "Edit Image" and wait for the preview.
   - Export the result in one click.
   - No login or signup required.
